Class PDFilterConfigurationException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • com.deltaxml.api.DeltaXMLException
          • com.deltaxml.cores9api.PDConfigurationException
            • com.deltaxml.cores9api.PDFilterConfigurationException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PDFilterConfigurationException
extends PDConfigurationException

    Indicates an error encountered when loading a filter defined in a Pipeline Description format, after parameters are resolved.

    The cause of the exception may be one of: FilterConfigurationException, FilterParameterizationException, NonUniqueParameterNameException.

    Since:
    7.2
